Iroquois Brands Ltd said it hasbeen sued by Lyon Food Cos Inc which is seeking 2.3 mln dlrs indamages in connection with the April 1986 nine mln dlrspurchase of Iroquois' former specialty food products segment.    Iroquois said that based upon the defenses it will assert,it does not believe that any charge against income is requiredas a result of the claim. Reuter&#3;